1926;;The Winning of Barbara Worth;;American;;Henry King;;Ronald Colman, Vilma BÃ¡nky, Gary Cooper;;western;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Winning_of_Barbara_Worth;;As a child, Barbara is orphaned when her settler parents perish trying to cross a California desert. She is rescued and raised by Jefferson Worth, who dreams of irrigating the desert. Fifteen years later, Willard Holmes, the chief engineer of a company intent on diverting the Colorado River to do just that, arrives and is smitten with Barbara. However, he has a rival for her affections: local cowboy Abe Lee.